*Pucao* je na zid. (He shot at the wall.)
On je *pucao* iz pištolja. (He shot from a pistol.)
Oni su *pucali* u zrak. (They shot into the air.)
Oni su se *puškom* pucali. (They were shooting at each other with a gun.)
Njegov pištolj je *pucao* iznenada. (His pistol suddenly went off.)
Neko je *pucnuo* u daljini. (Someone fired in the distance.)